name: Pinky Gems
description:
This "gem" is a great statement piece to your wardrobe, it sparkles and shines just like any woman should. It has a floral pattern because flower patterns and prints are Rhea's favorite trend.

Other color's available, just email Rhea with your color preference.

name: "Golden Chic"
description:
Golden Chic will add a little bit of something extra to your wardrobe. Wear it with any plain black top or even a lace top and leather leggings and call it a day out with your girl friends! Great for a day to night look.

Also comes in Silver and black. 

Materials:
Gold Beads hand sewn onto black felt base.
Gold Chain and clasp.

name: Glam Me Up with Pearls
description:
Glam up with pearls for a girly look with the peter pan collar inspiration. Looks lovely with a Little Black Dress. You will definitely look Chic.

Other colors available please request by email.

Materials: 
White Small and Large round pearls hand sewn onto fabric felt.
Silver chain with clasp.

name: "Ruby" Peter Pan inspired collar Necklace
description:
Dazzle in this "Ruby" necklace. Just the perfect touch to add A Little Bit of Chic to your wardrobe.

Materials:
Red sequins and red pearls hand sewn onto fabric felt.
